    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "he's actually getting pretty annoyed with all the fussing and just wants to lie down. he says he feels fine if he stays still. if i just give him some aspirin and let him nap for a few hours to see if he wakes up feeling better, would that be okay? he really doesn't want to go to a hospital if it's just travel fatigue.",
